ElementValuePresence, OptionSelected
public abstract class StringCondition
extends AbstractElementCondition<String>

Parent class for ExpectedCondition implementations that rely on the presence of a WebElement and return a string value. If one of the internal checks fails, the failure message is reported in the AbstractElementCondition.message property.

Volker Bergmann
